</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-08-02-0232-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-08-02-0232-fn-0001">1</a>
 
   <p>On 28 June GW paid Boucher 75 for John Parke Custiss schooling, and Custis went to Bouchers in Annapolis on 26 July. See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-08-02-0231" class="document">Cash Accounts, June 1770</a>, <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Donald Jackson and Dorothy Twohig, eds. &lt;i&gt;The Diaries of George Washington&lt;/i&gt;. 6 vols. Charlottesville, Va., 197679. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Diaries</span></span>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-01-02-02-0005-0018#GEWN-01-02-02-pb-0256" class="document">2:256</a>, and Guardian Accounts, 28 June 1770.</p>

